      <h1 class='title'>Sixth Forms</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c86WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_86ws' title='Col. 86WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c86WS' name='column_86ws' href='#column_86ws' rel='bookmark'>86WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05091'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_440'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-damian-green' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_440' title='Link to this speech by Mr Damian Green' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-damian-green" title="Mr Damian Green">Mr. Damian Green</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05091">To ask the Secretary of State for Education and Skills how many schools have<span class="italic">(a)</span> opened and <span class="italic">(b)</span> closed sixth forms since 1997. [133693]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-05092'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_441'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-ivan-lewis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_441' title='Link to this speech by Mr Ivan Lewis' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-ivan-lewis" title="Mr Ivan Lewis">Mr. Ivan Lewis</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-05092">Since 1997 73 new school sixth forms have opened and 26 school sixth forms have closed.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
